    <h2> The Providence Online: Echo of the Mirror Shards (Act V)</h2>
    <p>
        <br />Welcome to SHARDSTREAM's official website.
        <br />The game is not available yet, and is still in early development, but more content will be added here as we create it.</p>
    <br />
    <h2>What is SHARDSTREAM?</h2>
    <p>SHARDSTREAM is an independant upcoming video game created by the team of Fractal Hexagon. It is a tactical RPG inspired by <a href="http://www.wikiwand.com/en/Final_Fantasy_Tactics_Advance ">Final Fantasy Tactics Advance</a>, <a href="http://www.wikiwand.com/en/Advance_Wars ">Advance Wars</a>, and some elements of <a href="http://www.wikiwand.com/en/Fire_Emblem ">Fire Emblem</a>, <a href="http://www.civilization.com/ ">Civilization</a>, <a href="http://www.wikiwand.com/en/Disgaea ">Disgaea</a>, <a href="http://www.wikiwand.com/en/Metal_Gear_Solid:_Peace_Walker ">Metal Gear Solid: Peace Walker</a> and <a href="https://www.wikiwand.com/en/Descent:_Journeys_in_the_Dark ">Descent: Journeys in the Dark</a>. It will be released on Steam. The game will be set in the universe of the Providence Online novels and will be a sequel to it. It will be moddable and uses the Unity 5 engine, and is also open sourced.</p>
    <p>You can participate in the game's development if you know what you're doing by heading over to our <a href="https://github.com/FractalHexagon/SHARDSTREAM ">GitHub</a> page, <a href="mailto:fractalhexagon@gmail.com ">or sending us an email</a> to draw artwork for the game.
